---
name: Process / decision flow
category: Process
tags: [flowchart, decision, runbook]
description: Pure flowchart — start, decision, parallel branches, stop. Great for runbooks and onboarding flows.
---
# Process flowchart

nodes:
  - id: start, kind: start,    label: Start
  - id: input, kind: service,  label: "Collect input"
  - id: chk,   kind: decision, shape: diamond, label: "Valid?"
  - id: ok,    kind: service,  label: "Process"
  - id: fix,   kind: service,  label: "Show errors"
  - id: done,  kind: stop,     label: End

edges:
  - start -> input
  - input -> chk
  - chk   -> ok,   label: "yes"
  - chk   -> fix,  label: "no", kind: error
  - fix   -> input, kind: dashed, label: "retry"
  - ok    -> done
